{"tid":2141241,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"(驚變新疆而家要走)已有人提議組隊移民英國互助謀生","createTime":"2020-08-05T13:41:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T14:19:06.000Z","uid":326037,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d4c04180cc3b73a0569a858fc9513d8faaf0888a","tid":2141241,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T13:41:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RVT0X2jBJwA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRVT0X2jBJwA&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F2hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=ff990ada\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RVT0X2jBJwA</a><br />\n英國老人院 02/08/2020 BNO移居英國手冊之英國需求較大的低技術工作選擇<br />\n大家可以入去 英國老人院 講果個網睇下<br />\n居英論壇: <a href=\"https://HKers.co.uk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2FHKers.co.uk&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F2hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=051d3137\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://HKers.co.uk</a><br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------<br />\n有冇人想去英國搞速遞代購?<br />\n生意黎講應該叫做易起頭，又唔駛太多資本，有即時現金流番，仲係勞力密集，有大量廉價港裔新移民供應請埋義士都得<br />\n<br />\n香港人有錢有腦 為何不建小香港圍爐落腳自助 僱用英國本地居民幫自己移民並為英國經濟作出即時貢獻<br />\n<br />\n西式建築<br />\n港式裝修<br />\n英語環境<br />\n香港特色<br />\n買地創業<br />\n提供就業<br />\n請埋白人<br />\n即時貢獻<br />\n<br />\n如果當自己係香港人 希望去英國承擔公民責任 行使天賦自由權利<br />\n就應建小香港圍爐落腳自助 因為300萬人有機會去 到時當地不堪負擔<br />\n當地藍到黑舊移民/極右一定合力搞死香港新移民<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------<br />\n引用下維新志士的文，好似香港人而家的處境<br />\n【絕不放棄】1848年，德國革命失敗，接近500萬德國人逃亡，<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2135081/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2135081/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxsz8AWA.jpg&amp;h=551e487f&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n▲德國移民係美國建起既城，威斯康星州．密爾沃基(Milwaukee) <span class=\"gold\">(美國都比起小德國)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F06Azwut.jpg&amp;h=6804b467&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n▲圖為1922年北美的德語報紙。從1850年代起，德裔移民就已經帶來了不少德語報紙。在1894年，在美國刊行的德語報紙達到了最高鋒的800份。<span class=\"gold\">(美國都比用德文)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1bRV0s1.png&amp;h=d8a48b2e&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n▲德裔為最大族裔的地區 <span class=\"gold\">(美國最多係德裔)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F36LLDeM.jpg&amp;h=ff932211&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n▲18歲的Frederick Trump。他才剛到了北美2年。<span class=\"gold\">(第一代去到就搞地產 香港人專長)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F07%2F29%2F223537_42bc50c7104b2124d1e6de3887df3798.png&amp;h=c59b1ed9&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n他有一個兒子，叫Fred Trump，是紐約的地產大亨。<span class=\"gold\">(第二代已極富)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE8SBKUU.jpg&amp;h=4b463e18&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n他的兒子，就是今天第45任美國總統，Donald J. Trump。<span class=\"gold\">(第三代做總統)</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><p class=\"center\"><span class=\"xx-large\">*****效法*****<br />\n<br />\n德國人<br />\n意大利人<br />\n波蘭人<br />\n美國人</span></p></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國係民主國家 亦係移民國家 應該追求自由 不受種族限制<br />\n不是去到英國就要跟英國果套文化 應該發展香港文化 多元包容先可以發揮移民優勢<br />\n否則香港人去到英文又唔夠好 技術又唔識 錢又冇 成世做中餐館廉價奴工<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">邊到有香港人 香港就係邊到光復</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZhE5PuG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZhE5PuG.png&h=586a486b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb68e21b756007b82a80c27304bffdebe352d57d","tid":2141241,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T23:21:20.000Z","msg":"而家越睇越唔駛走 新八國聯軍再起 係香港就能見到自由自在"},{"pid":"4a43e0e14499d734ebbcfbcf2c5d918773d886d1","tid":2141241,"uid":215876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T23:44:15.000Z","msg":"你開過好多次post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9066f888d6072701013aea71f1d66b6bd862851","tid":2141241,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4a43e0e14499d734ebbcfbcf2c5d918773d886d1","tid":2141241,"uid":215876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T23:44:15.000Z","msg":"你開過好多次post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:18:30.000Z","msg":"?"},{"pid":"990556b5069011460a81a0662d878a45920d7ee1","tid":2141241,"uid":57237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:48:58.000Z","msg":"呢度有人有錢買地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d2f8951035daecc84efbe4f09da94dc18560d8","tid":2141241,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"990556b5069011460a81a0662d878a45920d7ee1","tid":2141241,"uid":57237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:48:58.000Z","msg":"呢度有人有錢買地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T14:19:06.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n612/星火/我要攬炒登報"}]}